div.p:
¶Conſider how much longer or ſhorter your day propoſed is then 12 houres, and take the difference, then the proportion will be;





As the Sine of 90 degrees,

Is to the Sine of halfe the difference;

So is the Tangent complement of the Latitude of the place,

To the Tangent of the declination that the Sun ſhall have

when the day is at ſuch a length as you require.
